WEBVTT

00:00:49.360 --> 00:00:50.160
Pay up!

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:51.840
No, no, brother, calm down.

00:01:04.360 --> 00:01:06.320
Zheng Nanfeng, give me back my job!

00:01:07.440 --> 00:01:08.240
Yadong.

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:10.160
What do you want with me?

00:01:10.440 --> 00:01:11.800
Why did you bring so many people?

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:13.080
What else could it be?

00:01:13.480 --> 00:01:14.480
With such a big show of force...

00:01:14.480 --> 00:01:15.800
...he's definitely here to take us down.

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:18.160
Boss Zheng is at the top in Haicheng.

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:20.000
How would I dare?

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:22.520
Boss Cheng.

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:24.640
You deliberately chose the day of my launch event.

00:01:24.680 --> 00:01:25.560
You have an ulterior motive.

00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:26.440
Speak.
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:27.720
What do you really want?

00:01:28.440 --> 00:01:29.400
Boss Zheng.

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:30.760
Let me clarify something first.

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.880
These workers all came on their own.

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:34.280
My people...

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:35.560
...are also on strike.

00:01:36.360 --> 00:01:39.640
The dance halls, factories, real estate companies—all shut down.

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:41.160
We can't make a living anymore.

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.000
My brothers here definitely won't stand for it.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:43.640
Right?

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.760
We won't stand for it!

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:47.840
No! We won't!

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:48.840
Pay us back!

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.400
No!

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:51.400
Compensate us!

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.200
Boss Zheng.

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:55.240
Don't misunderstand me.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:57.400
I'm not here to fight you today.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.000
I'm here to discuss cooperation.

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:00.200
Cooperation?

00:02:01.160 --> 00:02:01.960
That's right.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:03.000
I heard...

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:05.280
...you've developed an international logistics business.

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:07.840
Today's the signing ceremony, right?

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:10.440
Well, I spent some time abroad.

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:13.480
I know a fair bit about international logistics and transport.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:16.000
If you hand that work over to me...

00:02:16.280 --> 00:02:18.440
...won't my brothers have food on the table?

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:21.840
Alright.

00:02:22.040 --> 00:02:23.200
Or not.

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:25.280
It's up to Boss Zheng.

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:32.200
Alright.

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:33.160
Brother Feng.

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:34.640
You brought so many men...

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.800
...I don't dare say no.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:37.600
It's just...

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:41.000
I have a bit of a headache right now.

00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:45.200
My banquet hall...

00:02:45.320 --> 00:02:46.600
...didn't prepare that much liquor.

00:02:47.440 --> 00:02:49.280
To our future cooperation!

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:50.200
Come on.

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:51.400
A toast to Boss Zheng!

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:57.160
When are you planning to change how you address him?

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:00.680
Bottoms up!

00:03:49.760 --> 00:03:51.200
Take it easy on the drinks.

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:52.520
You don't listen.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:54.600
Don't.

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.000
I told you to drink less.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.280
Don't show off.

00:03:57.480 --> 00:03:58.280
You insisted on drinking.

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:00.240
Over here.

00:04:05.800 --> 00:04:06.880
Careful.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:31.200
Welcome back, boss!

00:04:35.840 --> 00:04:36.480
Sis.

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:42.800
Jiachang.

00:04:44.440 --> 00:04:47.200
Let A-Jie properly wash away your bad luck.

00:04:50.080 --> 00:04:50.880
Come on, boss.

00:04:57.960 --> 00:04:58.560
Let's go.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.880
We've arranged a welcome banquet for you today.

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:02.560
At the Waterside Hotel.

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:12.640
Five years.

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:14.600
A full five years.

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:16.000
Brother Xie.

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:16.800
Sis.

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:19.240
Do you know how I've lived these five years?

00:05:19.800 --> 00:05:21.280
It's still more comfortable outside.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:23.960
How great it is out here.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.960
Enjoy yourself properly, Jiachang.

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:32.960
Head up to the third floor in a bit.

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:34.680
We've arranged a welcome banquet for you.

00:05:36.640 --> 00:05:38.200
These five years...

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:39.920
...I definitely didn't suffer for nothing.

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:41.600
Jiachang, what do you mean by that?

00:05:41.960 --> 00:05:43.040
This debt...

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:45.280
...I will definitely settle with Zheng Nanfeng.

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:47.760
I'll pay it back tenfold, a hundredfold.

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:50.800
You still want to fight Zheng Nanfeng, is that it?

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.600
From now on, in Haicheng, it's either him or me.

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:53.400
Either me or him.

00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:56.600
Listen to me for a moment.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.800
Neither of us is a match for Zheng Nanfeng.

00:05:59.000 --> 00:05:59.960
The harder you fight...

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:01.080
...the faster it backfires.

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:01.960
Sis.

00:06:01.960 --> 00:06:03.080
How is that the same?

00:06:03.200 --> 00:06:04.480
I'm out now.

00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:05.880
This is us, brother and sister, joining forces.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:07.960
We must make sure he ends up with nowhere to be buried.

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:13.680
Zheng Nanfeng repaid evil with good.

00:06:14.600 --> 00:06:15.760
Not only did he not hold a grudge...

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:18.200
...he helped our company come back from the brink.

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:21.040
I don't want to fight him anymore.

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.280
Sis.

00:06:23.640 --> 00:06:24.880
Am I hearing you right?

00:06:25.400 --> 00:06:27.160
Hearing this from you...

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:32.000
So I'm advising you to back down too.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:32.400
Okay?

00:06:34.040 --> 00:06:34.760
Impossible.

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:35.560
Jiachang.

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:38.960
Don't you see Cheng Yadong is cooperating with him now too?

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:40.760
Think about it carefully.

00:06:40.760 --> 00:06:42.600
I really don't want to see anything happen to you.

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:44.160
What else could possibly happen to me?

00:06:44.760 --> 00:06:45.560
Huh?

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:47.800
You think I'm still the same person I was before?

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:49.560
I can take him down without you.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.200
Jiachang, listen to me.

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:52.000
Sis.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:55.000
I've always looked up to you.

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:58.040
I never thought you'd be scared out of your wits like this.

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.960
My stance remains the same.

00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:03.600
From now on, in this world...

00:07:03.600 --> 00:07:04.840
...it's either him or me.

00:07:05.760 --> 00:07:06.800
Either me or him.

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:21.480
Boss.

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:24.320
Boss.

00:07:25.760 --> 00:07:26.960
I want to follow you again.

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:31.000
Boss.

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:33.480
Even though I've been working for Big Sis lately...

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:35.400
...I've been waiting for you to get out.

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:37.600
No matter what...

00:07:37.600 --> 00:07:38.280
...I'm with you.

00:07:41.240 --> 00:07:42.640
It seems I didn't misjudge you after all.

00:07:43.640 --> 00:07:44.520
Boss.

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:46.240
You raised me from the ground up.

00:07:46.840 --> 00:07:48.200
I know what needs to be done.

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:51.960
Tell me...

00:07:51.960 --> 00:07:53.360
...what's going on with my sister?

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:55.240
How did she become a different person?

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:57.880
It's a long story.

00:07:58.280 --> 00:07:59.160
Here's the plan.

00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:00.840
I'll take you for a sauna first.

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:02.240
Then I'll tell you everything slowly.

00:08:03.680 --> 00:08:04.240
Let's go.

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:24.000
Boss

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:24.840
How's it going?

00:08:25.160 --> 00:08:27.080
We've added more men, everyone's busy.

00:08:27.440 --> 00:08:28.480
The client is pushing for the goods.

00:08:28.640 --> 00:08:30.080
Tell the brothers to hurry up.

00:08:30.440 --> 00:08:31.960
We absolutely cannot delay them.

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.160
Don't ruin our reputation.

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:33.600
Yes.

00:08:33.720 --> 00:08:35.080
Don't worry, Boss, we won't mess up.

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:35.760
Alright.

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.600
There shouldn't be any problems, right?

00:08:45.400 --> 00:08:46.640
The whole port is running smoothly.

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:48.200
He handles operations quite skillfully too.

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:49.360
I really didn't expect that.

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:52.200
So we're really handing the logistics business to him?

00:08:52.640 --> 00:08:54.840
I already said it to his face.

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:57.240
And after observing these past few days, there are no issues.

00:08:57.240 --> 00:08:58.080
Let's give it to him.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:08:59.400
I'll have Aqiang keep an eye on things.

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:01.800
Fine.

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:04.000
Alright.

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:04.640
Let's head back.

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:06.120
The food stall?

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:07.400
What food stall?

00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:07.960
We're going home.

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:09.200
I'll cook a couple of dishes for you.

00:09:10.040 --> 00:09:10.760
Okay.

00:09:10.760 --> 00:09:12.240
Whatever Sister Zhiyi says.

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:14.200
Drive, Nanfeng.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.760
The boss is gone.

00:09:24.440 --> 00:09:26.200
Tell the brothers to pause what they're doing.

00:09:28.040 --> 00:09:29.040
Everyone head to Warehouse Four.

00:09:30.040 --> 00:09:30.840
Yes.

00:09:31.840 --> 00:09:32.640
Let's go.

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:39.600
Boss.

00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:41.400
These all came from overseas.

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.360
Genuine goods.

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:43.600
Top-notch quality.

00:09:43.880 --> 00:09:45.080
They're in high demand on the market.

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:47.160
Get the goods loaded.

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:48.800
You two handle the delivery personally.

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:50.640
Don't let anyone at the company know.

00:09:50.960 --> 00:09:51.760
Understood.

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:57.040
Mr. Cheng, I've been looking everywhere for you.

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:59.600
You haven't signed for the goods that just arrived.

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:07.000
Mr. Cheng.

00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:07.800
This is...

00:10:09.080 --> 00:10:10.600
You're not careful at all.

00:10:11.240 --> 00:10:12.800
You got the container data wrong.

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:14.520
No, it's correct.

00:10:14.520 --> 00:10:16.040
I checked it carefully.

00:10:16.040 --> 00:10:17.440
258 containers.

00:10:18.760 --> 00:10:20.400
It's clearly 248.

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:22.400
Isn't this it?

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:24.160
This is a last-minute order.

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:25.280
It's not on the master list.

00:10:25.800 --> 00:10:26.600
Don't count it.

00:10:27.160 --> 00:10:29.240
Okay, I'll have someone open and inspect them right away.

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:30.600
No inspection needed.

00:10:30.680 --> 00:10:32.160
I already had them checked.

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:33.240
Time is tight.

00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:34.600
Don't delay the transfer.

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:36.400
But this doesn't follow procedure.

00:10:36.760 --> 00:10:37.560
Enough nonsense.

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:38.680
Do as Mr. Cheng says.

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:39.400
Hey.

00:10:39.880 --> 00:10:41.240
Watch your tone.

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:43.000
You can trust me to handle things.

00:10:43.760 --> 00:10:44.840
Yes, Mr. Cheng.

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:45.800
Just create a new order.

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:00.800
Go on.

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:05.840
Get back to work.

00:11:05.840 --> 00:11:06.400
Alright.

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:14.200
I didn't expect...

00:11:14.320 --> 00:11:15.960
...that during my absence...

00:11:16.440 --> 00:11:17.640
...so much would happen.

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:18.800
I think...

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:21.800
...Big Sister was just momentarily bewitched by Zheng Nanfeng.

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:23.280
Brother.

00:11:23.280 --> 00:11:25.360
Let's try to talk some sense into Big Sister later.

00:11:25.400 --> 00:11:27.200
She might just change her mind.

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:29.760
Not necessarily.

00:11:30.280 --> 00:11:31.160
What do you mean?

00:11:31.800 --> 00:11:33.560
I know my sister's personality.

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:35.760
Once she's set her mind on something...

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:37.440
...she won't change it.

00:11:38.360 --> 00:11:39.880
Getting her to change her mind now...

00:11:40.960 --> 00:11:42.560
...won't be easy.

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:43.160
No, but...

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:45.040
Even if we can't convince her...

00:11:45.080 --> 00:11:47.000
...once we go up against Zheng Nanfeng...

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:49.280
...Big Sister can't possibly not side with you.

00:11:49.280 --> 00:11:51.200
After all, you're blood siblings.

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:53.000
We'll see.

00:11:56.160 --> 00:11:57.520
But just now, hearing you talk about...

00:11:57.520 --> 00:11:58.720
...Cheng Yadong's situation...

00:11:59.160 --> 00:12:00.480
...I find it quite interesting.

00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:03.640
Speaking of him...

00:12:03.800 --> 00:12:05.280
...I'm a bit puzzled too.

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:06.920
You said he was once a big name in Haicheng.

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:08.560
A real somebody.

00:12:08.800 --> 00:12:10.080
But now...

00:12:10.080 --> 00:12:11.800
...his wife was taken from him.

00:12:11.840 --> 00:12:13.200
And he actually has the nerve...

00:12:13.200 --> 00:12:14.320
...to go seek cooperation.

00:12:14.440 --> 00:12:16.800
He's become a joke among the brothers in the underworld.

00:12:19.040 --> 00:12:20.680
I don't think it's that simple.

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:24.440
Here's what we'll do.

00:12:25.160 --> 00:12:26.080
You go arrange a meeting with him.

00:12:26.400 --> 00:12:27.400
I'll meet with him.

00:12:29.000 --> 00:12:31.600
Is that even necessary now?

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:36.880
Haven't you heard the saying?

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:39.200
The enemy of my enemy...

00:12:39.560 --> 00:12:41.080
...is my friend.

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:48.800
I miss you.

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:52.720
Whenever dusk arrives.

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:56.600
The evening breeze rises.

00:12:58.200 --> 00:13:00.440
Missing you.

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:04.440
Life's mysteries.

00:13:05.960 --> 00:13:08.560
Try not to see them clearly.

00:13:10.360 --> 00:13:12.960
Close your eyes.

00:13:14.280 --> 00:13:16.160
Don't respond.

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:22.160
The evening breeze blows and blows.

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:24.840
Go with the wind.

00:13:27.640 --> 00:13:30.280
Tonight, child, don't cry in secret.

00:13:31.080 --> 00:13:34.440
Don't cry in secret.

00:13:34.440 --> 00:13:38.280
The evening breeze blows and blows.

00:13:38.280 --> 00:13:40.960
Go with the wind.

00:13:42.800 --> 00:13:46.120
With the night's curtain of stars.

00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:50.120
Gently fall asleep.

00:13:50.120 --> 00:13:52.560
Blow, evening breeze.